ratings.question_text: What is your overall assessment of this course?

narratives.question_text: How would you summarize AFAM 505 01/AMST 643 01 for a fellow student? Would you recommend AFAM 505 01/AMST 643 01 to another student? Why or why not?
comments: Good for intro to biochem scientific paper reading; i feel this course is very much needed--especially for physician scientists, but it could have been taught bettert (i.e. discussions could have been facilitated better with fewer papers to read)

narratives.question_text: How did this course deepen your knowledge of your discipline/profession? To what extent did this course contribute to your dissertation/research?
comments: Great intro to valuable biochemical techniques. Also, I like that were introduced to strong as well as flawed ways to exercise the empirical method. I wish newer basic science techniquescould have been more well-emphasized
